‼️TRUCK UPDATE‼️This is well overdue and I figured there is no better time than now since SEMA is one week away. Many of you may remember I purchased this truck over 2 years ago to build for the SEMA show in 2021. I was beyond thrilled to turn another dream into reality. I had really big plans for this one! I couldn’t wait and was so excited that just after 3 days of owning it we started stripping everything down. I was able to get a couple of big name companies that jumped on board as major sponsors which made me feel like we started this build with really good momentum. However, all of that came to a halt. Unfortunately one of the major sponsors that had agreed to help out with this project ended up leading me down a dead end road for over a year. I gave them the benefit of the doubt because during this timeline we were in the middle of peak Covid. So I knew everything in the industry was fukd. However, after countless back and forth emails I kept hearing that my parts were still being manufactured and it was going to ship out at the end of the month. Every time I heard this it gave me hope. Until I heard this for a year straight. In hindsight, if I would have just bought everything my self it would have been finished. But this was around $40k worth of product so, of course I didn’t want to if I didn’t have to. Anyways to wrap things up this really bummed me out and after already spending thousands and thousands of dollars on shit for a truck that’s sat on a lift for 2 years straight. I eventually lost all motivation and decided it was time to move on. As of a couple months ago the truck has since been put back to stock and was sold last week. Sorry to everyone who was looking forward to seeing this build come to life. It’s time to move on and start fresh. I will be getting back into the truck game and by doing so I just purchased one of the coolest trucks ever today for the next build. 
Reveal coming tomorrow. 🐛✌🏼
